This paper proposes a networking solution for 5G scenarios, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The proposed solution involves the use of intelligent decision-making algorithms (cs.AI) and a learning system (cs.LG) to optimize network performance. The paper also mentions security (cs.CR) and software-defined networking (cs.DC) as related topics.
